[I] Ruby manual builder

[T] Builds manuals. It converts simple, human readable textfiles to roff for
[T] terminal display, and also to HTML for the web.

[U] https://github.com/rtomayko/ronn

[A] Ryan Tomayko <http://github.com/rtomayko>
[A] Chris Wanstrath <http://github.com/defunkt>
[A] Suraj N. Kurapati <http://github.com/sunaku>
